52: /**
53:  * DefaultChannel is the default {@link Channel}.
54:  * <p/>
55:  * The current implementation is just a composite containing the interceptors and error handler that beforehand was
56:  * added to the route graph directly. <br/>
57:  * With this {@link Channel} we can in the future implement better strategies for routing the {@link Exchange} in the
58:  * route graph, as we have a {@link Channel} between each and every node in the graph.
59:  */
